data.description: Care of ownership in this over 1700 square foot 3-bedroom 2.5 bathrooms, private garage with a brick paver entry.  This home was done right with upscale cabinets, granite counter tops and full granite backsplashes, ceramic tile in bathrooms and on main floor. Walk-in closets, and custom color paint throughout. With limited availability, the popular community of Copper Oaks features a clubhouse, resort-style pool and recreation area. With a premium location close to shopping, dining, airport and all that sunny southwest Florida has to offer. Schedule your private showing today!
